									eMenu is a new service, that includes both a platform for restaurants to insert information related with their activity, but also a mobile application where the clients can consult information.<br>							
									The two main components are:<br><br>
									<ul><ul>
										<li>&#9658 <b>The Restaurants:</b><br><br>
